interestingcomments.content: 55-200 vs 50-230 /!/ Going to iceland in a month, have the xt3 preordered. Current set up is the 18-55, 16, and 35/ 1.4. Want to get some reach while for the trip. I noticed that on ebay i can get the 50-230 from taiwan for real cheap but i noticed higher f stop and can make the assumption the build suffers. I really am more interested in the IQ the lens produces, from what i can tell on IG from looking at tags, the 55-200 looks better and probably regarded the better lens, but obviously 2x the price at least. Just wanted to hear some people who have the lens recommendations and feedback, cheers!
